imdb.plot outline: Dimity Esber is a great actress, yet admirably always searching for that greater performance she knows she has in her. She likes the finer things in life, particularly biodynamic juices and caviar, because she needs to be in shape, and while she doesn't model anymore because models are talentless leeches, she always wants to be able to convincingly play a model on screen. There are rumors she uses performance enhancing drugs for her award-winning roles. She also isn't sure who she's dating currently, and reading the tabloids is confusing her more. She's a passionate feminist with and entrepreneurial spirit and a soft spot for animals and knows her obscure world cinema well. Vogue says "She's so hip she could have hipatitis!" Dimity Esber is Australia's hottest young film star and entrepreneur.
